title: American_Top_20_Special_December_15th,_2001_Christmas
description:
"This is Casey counting down your favorite holiday hits. From Mistletoe, Kentucky, to Wreath Hill, Wyoming; from Poinsettia Park, Florida, to Holly Branch, Delaware, from Reindeer Lake, Alaska, to Rudolph Run, West Virginia; from Noel, Colorado, to Merry Christmas Creek, Alaska,

"From Peace, Alaska, to Bethlehem, Pennsylvania, these are the songs that lift our spirits and fill our hearts during the holiday season.

"From Santa Claus, Nevada, to North Pole, New York. Really! We're counting down the best of the holiday classics; I'm Casey Kasem."


This is a rebroadcast of a countdown show hosted by Casey Kasem subsequent to AT40. The show was called American Top 20. I'm pretty sure the original air date was December 15th, 2001.

This is one to have playing when friends and family come over.
